data.description: Welcome to your coastal oasis in Seabrook, Texas! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home embodies luxury and comfort in a waterfront community. With a spacious living room, open kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances, and access to a covered patio, entertaining is effortless. The first-floor primary bedroom offers a serene retreat with a large bathroom and closet. Upstairs, three additional bedrooms await. Outside, enjoy the fully fenced backyard. Plus, indulge in HOA amenities including a pool, tennis and volleyball courts, a boat ramp, and a playground. Don't miss out on this slice of paradise – schedule your tour today!
